<br>
Either way, people who bitch at clerics make me rethink why I play my class.  There really is not a whole lot of gratification to being a cleric.  And some days, those people who bitch at clerics really makes you want to just stop playing your class.<br>
<br>
As a cleric, I really have alot of respect for all of the clerics who stick with thier characters.  Its alot of work, alot of dedication, and alot of patience for very small amounts of gratitude. <p><br>
