<br>
Even as only a level 20 shaman, I receive countless requests for SoW and buffs.  Those requestors are often quick to become offended, demanding, and downright bitchy and offensIVE.  I can only imagine what clerics go through every time they log in.<br>
<br>
So, thank you, clerics, for putting up with all of us, and persevering, despite the abuse, harassment, and general aggravation of it all.<br>
<br>
